{"tid":1932602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誰是媽媽最愛的兒子？CNN新聞直播演變成了兄弟二人爭寵吵架現場……","createTime":"2020-03-18T22:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T00:01:25.000Z","uid":10199,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38be5a6a460066ce4bcc73396f75f187e3606db8","tid":1932602,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:28:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hviwAJjIeKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhviwAJjIeKc&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=50d3ddf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hviwAJjIeKc</a><br />\n這段CNN新聞直播演變成了兄弟二人爭寵吵架現場&hellip;&hellip;CNN主播和州長直播爭寵<br />\n<br />\nCNN主播Chris Cuomo昨天在節目中連線紐約州長Andrew Cuomo，討論紐約州應對新冠肺炎的方案。你可能已經發現了，這兩個人姓氏一樣：沒錯，這兩位還有另外一層關係&mdash;&mdash;親兄弟。<br />\n<br />\n談話結尾階段，Chris主播不知道哪根筋不對，突然提醒對方：「不管你多忙，都要記得給媽媽打電話。」<br />\n<br />\nAndrew州長好像也抽風了，竟然說：「我不僅打過電話了，而且她告訴我，我是她最愛的兒子。好消息是，她說你排第二。」<br />\n<br />\n（此時此刻的觀眾：？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？？）<br />\n<br />\nChris主播接下來話茬：「媽媽從來不給我們排名，我不敢相信你竟然對我的觀眾說謊！早知道我該掐了直播的！」<br />\n<br />\nAndrew州長又重複：「第二寵愛的孩子，請聽清楚哦。」<br />\n<br />\n嗯，這是真的CNN直播，不是惡搞&hellip;&hellip;怎麼還帶這麼玩的？"},{"pid":"f37041abb821e76931396eb4a3fcb8571c08309d","tid":1932602,"uid":312333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:32:44.000Z","msg":"新你老母，武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"8a40aa53ccec1612b83db2c1787731c6243d9699","tid":1932602,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T23:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afecbab0a5a3efc7fa2a414dc7decb38bdf287d7","tid":1932602,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T23:22:26.000Z","msg":"America~ Fuck yeah!!"},{"pid":"7103cf98a91280d8b4139355b7054d5004b8aff5","tid":1932602,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"